      "content": "woah okay that sounds really intense. i didnt realize it was that serious. but i've heard from a few people that since its just a herbal supplement it shouldn't affect the meds that much? like, i was only thinking of taking a small dose, not a ton. are you sure it's actually life-threatening even if I don't take much?",
